WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:03:55.039
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:59.121
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for joining me again today.

00:03:59.123 --> 00:04:04.679
I just want to tell y'all thank you for joining us and praying with us and being here so promptly.

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:13.294
I'm going to go over some things from what the Lord showed us in this last video, but I want to say this right off the bat: I have to apologize.

00:04:13.295 --> 00:04:26.362
I was corrected by the Spirit of the Lord today. I went about last night, some of the things I said and how I criticized President Trump, and the Lord said I dishonored him.

00:04:26.363 --> 00:04:36.509
I want to say this: I apologize for my opinion and how I present myself and some of the things I say when I criticize him.

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:46.908
Because of things that the Lord had talked to me privately about, I brought them up publicly, and there were things that I shouldn't have said.

00:04:46.909 --> 00:04:57.097
Me and Him, we have these conversations, but what we say doesn't mean it's for the public. Does that make sense?

00:04:57.098 --> 00:05:06.359
Like my wife and I have conversations we don't bring out in public; you just have private conversations. That's the way it is with the Lord.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:15.637
There are certain things I said about his voting and the past that I owe apologies for, and the Lord corrected me very sternly.

00:05:15.637 --> 00:05:31.586
He said, 'Brandon, the more your platform has influence and the more it grows, you're going to be held accountable more and more for what you say. You can't just flippantly say things out of your mouth.

00:05:31.587 --> 00:05:40.522
This is a public forum; there are millions of people watching.'So, for everybody in the government, I'm going to tell you this: I apologize for how I handle myself sometimes.

00:05:40.523 --> 00:05:44.839
You know what I'm learning? I'm growing and I am immature in how I handle some things.

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:53.525
I just want to say that I ask you to overlook certain things. I'm growing—growing pains is what I want to call it.

00:05:53.526 --> 00:05:56.322
Was that anybody else telling me to say that? No, it was the Holy Spirit.

00:05:56.323 --> 00:06:12.696
He corrected me very sternly today. I was out letting my dog go to the bathroom, and the Lord corrected me. It was a very heavy correction.

00:06:12.697 --> 00:06:22.327
So, anytime the Lord corrects me to the strength that He did today, I want to always be quick to repent and make it right.

00:06:22.328 --> 00:06:34.258
I don't even know if I could make that right other than just say, 'Listen, I was wrong.'My opinion and the conversations I have with the Father just need to—I need to learn how to filter better.

00:06:34.259 --> 00:06:39.997
So, like I said, with all that being said, I pray for grace from all y'all.

00:06:39.998 --> 00:06:48.851
There was not even anybody who said anything. It was interesting; it was just from the Lord.

00:06:48.852 --> 00:06:57.904
But I'm always quick to make it right. Be quick to repent and turn from things when the Holy Spirit corrects you.

00:06:57.905 --> 00:07:09.694
In doing so, I've continued to do that. That's why I believe that if you keep a heart right before Him, He'll keep using you.

00:07:09.695 --> 00:07:30.572
Now, praying over President Trump's decisions and the council, when I heard him talking about Taiwan and China—can you make sure what's that beeping noise in the back?

00:07:30.572 --> 00:07:56.275
It's really loud. Do you hear the beep, beep, beep? When I heard in the meeting what was being said, President Trump confirmed what we heard in the Spirit 24 hours ago. He confirmed it today in the news.

00:07:56.276 --> 00:08:31.839
It was told that Xi Jinping asked him directly—the president of China asked him directly—'Will you stand in resistance if we take Taiwan?'and President Trump would not answer.

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:45.239
And you're about to hear that. So, what did I hear? I heard that China was going to take Taiwan as we took Cuba in the days ahead.

00:08:45.240 --> 00:09:00.258
I saw the President liberating Cuba in the days ahead, and that there would be a financial blessing over Cuba for the first time in decades.

00:09:00.259 --> 00:09:22.753
They would liberate the tyrant government that has been over them, and Rubio will slay his tens of thousands and the chameleon will slay his thousands, and there will be jealousy between the two as one rises up in the polls and people say, 'We want him.

00:09:22.754 --> 00:09:33.963
We want David as our president next.'The one will be jealous of it and he'll have his thousands, but the one will have his tens of thousands.

00:09:33.964 --> 00:09:39.519
And I saw him becoming very polished in the days ahead, Rubio.

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:51.879
And I saw an anointing on him, and I saw Byron, the black man that has the beard—I saw that God was putting an anointing on this man.

00:09:51.880 --> 00:10:01.839
And I saw the number 25%. The Lord said, 'There are things that need to be corrected, but it's not much.

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:12.559
I will use this man in the days ahead.'Do you know who I'm talking about? You can show his picture if you want, but I saw Byron.

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:24.039
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to touch his life.'I saw DeSantis was 50/50.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:41.639
He was not as good as what he portrays, but he was a 50/50 mix. And the Lord said Rubio was not; his heart was more pliable.

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:53.239
And He said, 'Pray for these men. I saw them becoming the cabinet of the next administration.'That's what I was praying for.

00:10:53.240 --> 00:11:00.692
I saw the African-American man. People get mad and say, 'Brandon, you say racial things.'Listen, I'm just a Southern boy.

00:11:00.693 --> 00:11:04.302
I don't know nothing about trying to be racist. I love all colors.

00:11:04.303 --> 00:11:15.074
I love blacks, whites, Chinese, Asians—I love all of you. Brandon Biggs doesn't have racism in his bones. I love you.

00:11:15.075 --> 00:11:21.879
It's because I'm trying to be politically correct, trying to talk in front of hundreds of thousands of people, and I may butcher things.

00:11:21.880 --> 00:11:26.686
Then people say, 'Well, we're not African-Americans; we're just Africans.'Well, I'm ignorant, okay?

00:11:26.687 --> 00:11:37.279
So forgive me. But I do the best I can with what I know. I saw this man rise up like a vice president in the days ahead.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:44.719
I saw that there would be a strong pull for him—this man right here.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:12:03.279
And the Lord said, 'Pray for him.'And that's when I was talking about the restoration and the restitution of making wrongs right for a true African-American who is going to rise up.

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:15.759
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to restore back what the cankerworm ate.'Obama had a white mama, but he's a true black man.

00:12:15.760 --> 00:12:24.759
And the Lord said, 'Watch what I do with this man.'And I saw a blessing on him.

00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:35.559
So you pray for him because with that target on you in the spirit realm, the enemy would try to derail it.

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:43.838
The enemy knows what's being prophesied and he doesn't want him to succeed. So we're going to pray for him.

00:12:43.839 --> 00:12:50.519
We pray for a covering over that man Byron, just like how I told you about President Trump.

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:58.797
God has him in the office, and the enemy does not want him to fulfill what God has called him to do.

00:12:58.798 --> 00:13:06.759
There's a covering over him, and He said he must make it across the finish line.

00:13:06.760 --> 00:13:14.679
There are things that God has appointed him to accomplish that have to be accomplished, and Cuba is one of them.

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:19.011
The Lord said, 'I'm going to liberate the people.'And I saw old grandmas praying.

00:13:19.012 --> 00:13:22.871
They had prayer shawls. They looked like they were Catholic nuns.

00:13:22.872 --> 00:13:32.439
And they were weeping before the Lord as there was liberation coming to set the people of Cuba free.

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:40.679
And the Lord said, 'In the days ahead, watch. Keep praying for what I'm about to do with Cuba.'Okay?

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:46.093
And we keep bringing that up. We keep bringing it up, and I said, "It's coming."The Lord keeps—the visions are very colorful.

00:13:46.094 --> 00:13:49.221
They're very, very vibrant. That means they're getting closer and closer.

00:13:49.222 --> 00:13:58.458
There's something about to happen. This is why the Lord keeps having us pray for this. But I saw Taiwan; I saw a two-year window.

00:13:58.459 --> 00:14:11.714
Do you remember I told you that I heard President Trump say—and I don't know if this was his thoughts, and I don't want to be invasive, but I heard it—"All we need is two years.

00:14:11.715 --> 00:14:18.971
We don't need their chips. We'll make our own chips. We will create chips in America.

00:14:18.972 --> 00:14:25.026
All we need now is two years and we will develop our own chips."Do you have it?

00:14:25.027 --> 00:14:27.998
Yeah. I don't know if he said all that, but yeah. You said chips.

00:14:27.999 --> 00:14:33.447
"We don't need..."Yeah. Well, I didn't say it because I'm trying to be careful.

00:14:33.447 --> 00:14:42.333
Yes. So, I'm saying it today. So, I saw a two-year window. I saw a two-year window.

00:14:42.334 --> 00:14:51.399
And the Lord said, "Do they?"And so I saw why President Trump was trying to keep the dragon at bay, cracking his whip.

00:14:51.400 --> 00:15:00.439
Okay? I saw China cracking his whip. Like, "Listen,"and then President Trump said, "We're 8,000 or 9,000 miles away.

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:14.402
We're a long way."That's why I said, "Pray for Hawaii. Pray for Hawaii because I saw a Pearl Harbor event taking place in Hawaii by China.

00:15:14.403 --> 00:15:21.673
It was Midway, a mid-ground for our bases there to go off and try to protect.

00:15:21.674 --> 00:15:36.987
So as I saw that protection there, it was a two-year window—praying over a two-year window because the Trump administration—praying over his covering over him—it has about two and a half years left.

00:15:36.988 --> 00:15:47.396
So what we would have left of what I'm seeing, what we're praying over, is China taking it, but we would have our own chips.

00:15:47.397 --> 00:16:04.559
And that was him manufacturing here in America: Texas, probably Oklahoma, whatever in the southern states where we're not crazy like some of the Democratic states are charging so many taxes.

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:10.568
So that's what we're trying to play or not because it's a distraction. Go ahead. Well, yeah.

00:16:10.569 --> 00:16:21.839
When I see it spinning, Trump wants to pull back and he'll start to focus on this.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:31.403
Oh, and I see Taiwan in the midst of it. I see Taiwan in the midst of it bartering pieces.

00:16:31.404 --> 00:16:39.639
Do you understand? Trump's going to make his own chips. Do you hear?

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:44.759
Trump's going to make his own chips. We don't need Taiwan. That's what he...

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:49.886
and I don't mean that trying to—Chapter 2: Find scriptures to stand on—I'm just telling you what I heard.

00:16:49.887 --> 00:17:09.239
I see it. We pray for the people of Taiwan. That's what we got to do. I'm just called to fear God, not man.

00:17:09.240 --> 00:17:20.740
So I got quiet because the Lord rebuked me right there and he said, "You fear me, not them."Because I was concerned about what Taiwan people would be saying because of what Trump had—about what he said.

00:17:20.741 --> 00:17:33.759
And so that's why I was correcting that because in my heart, I was thinking more about what they were thinking than the prophetic word of what the Lord was showing me, saying, "Trump, this is what Trump said: 'We don't need Taiwan.

00:17:33.760 --> 00:17:43.176
We have our own chips. All we need is two years. All we need is two years.'"And then I was more feeling about the people's feelings.

00:17:43.177 --> 00:17:48.314
And the Lord said, "Fear me, not them."And he corrected me. I'm just being real.

00:17:48.315 --> 00:17:58.519
That's what was going on right there. I got rebuked again right then. So the Lord showed us more about that.

00:17:58.520 --> 00:18:05.119
Now, this is what was said about Taiwan today and President Trump just had this meeting.

00:18:05.120 --> 00:18:09.223
Go ahead. But China made clear that Taiwan is very important to them.

00:18:09.224 --> 00:18:18.489
And after your first meeting here, President Xi's spokesman put out a statement to the media saying this: "The Taiwan question is the most important issue in China-US relations.

00:18:18.490 --> 00:18:23.337
If it is handled properly, the bilateral relationship will enjoy overall stability.

00:18:23.338 --> 00:18:32.529
Otherwise, the two countries will have clashes and even conflicts, putting the entire relationship in great jeopardy."You were still inside the meeting when that came out.

00:18:32.530 --> 00:18:38.024
That sounded almost like a threat. Was it communicated that way behind closed doors?

00:18:38.025 --> 00:18:43.888
No. And no, it wasn't. Not at all. But it has always been their most important issue. And it's not a takeover.

00:18:43.889 --> 00:18:52.722
They just don't want to see this place—we'll call it a place because nobody knows how to define it—but they don't want to see it go independent.

00:18:52.723 --> 00:19:02.454
They don't want to do it. And I think they probably would do something pretty harsh and then they would be met harshly and bad things will happen.

00:19:02.455 --> 00:19:08.314
So no, it's not that. We talked, by the way—last night we talked a whole night about that issue.

00:19:08.315 --> 00:19:12.990
I think I know more about Taiwan right now than I know about almost any country.

00:19:12.991 --> 00:19:20.897
He dominated the talk. It's always been his most important thing from the day I knew him years ago.

00:19:20.898 --> 00:19:27.201
I've known him now 11, 12 years. It's always been the biggest thing for him: Taiwan.

00:19:27.202 --> 00:19:33.883
Now with me, I don't think they'll do anything when I'm here. When I'm not here, I think they might, to be honest with you.

00:19:33.884 --> 00:19:43.109
So, I'm not sure that they do anything if it remained as is, but they have somebody there now that wants to go independent. Well, it's a risky thing when you go independent.

00:19:43.110 --> 00:19:50.479
You know, they're going independent because they want to get into a war and they want to—they figure they have the United States behind them.

00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:54.516
I'd like to see it stay the way it is. And I'll tell you something, I'll make a little news.

00:19:54.517 --> 00:20:02.832
I'd like to see everybody making chips over in Taiwan come to America because, to be honest with you, I think it's the greatest thing you can do because it's a heated situation.

00:20:02.833 --> 00:20:11.015
There's no question about it. And as you know, we have massive amounts of chip companies now from Taiwan already coming in.

00:20:11.016 --> 00:20:18.947
We expect to have 40 to 50% of the world chip business by the end of my term. And I think it should be even more than that.

00:20:18.947 --> 00:20:25.479
I think all of those chip companies—if they're smart, they're going to start heading to Arizona and the places where they're building.

00:20:25.480 --> 00:20:33.600
That's going to solve your problem. So do you see that? It's what we saw in the spirit. That was what I was seeing.

00:20:33.601 --> 00:20:41.012
And then they had the meeting and they had this interview, and this is what the Lord said: "We don't need Taiwan."That's what he was saying.

00:20:41.013 --> 00:20:49.279
"We have our own chips."And that was the whole reason why America was back in Taiwan. And they were moving into America.

00:20:49.280 --> 00:21:16.079
And that's why I said, "Pray for Taiwan,"because I saw them being—I saw a mother hen bringing the island to her, trying to infiltrate South Korea through the politics, through North Korea, through the Philippines, through all of Japan, trying to bring them in like a mother hen.

00:21:16.080 --> 00:21:19.492
And that's why I warned you—how many times do you remember me saying this?

00:21:19.493 --> 00:21:29.679
They said, "Watch what China does."And I saw China turning their back on the Ukraine-Russia thing that's going on.

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:34.265
And I saw—remember I said I see a panda bear? Then I saw a turtle.

00:21:34.266 --> 00:21:47.719
I saw a dove with a wounded chest. I saw two black crows. I saw a robin, and the robin had wounded the dove.

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:57.119
The two black crows were standing there by the dove, and they were looking at the dove that was perished on the ground with its heart ripped out.

00:21:57.120 --> 00:22:10.326
And I said this is symbolic of people. And I saw the panda turn its back upon Russia and Ukraine, and I said he was gazing towards Taiwan, and it said, "It's our time.

00:22:10.327 --> 00:22:14.938
We want to take Taiwan now."And Xi Jinping is talking about it, and that's all they're talking about.

00:22:14.939 --> 00:22:20.439
That was three weeks ago, two weeks ago at the most. Maybe it was last week.

00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:26.139
And I said, "You're going to see an acceleration concerning Taiwan in the days ahead. Pray over Taiwan.

00:22:26.140 --> 00:22:34.260
Watch."And now this is all they're—"Are you going to stand in our way if we do this?"Okay.

00:22:34.261 --> 00:22:48.199
But I saw as we took Cuba and liberated Cuba and made them prosperous and blessed and got rid of the government they have and set up hotels and churches and blessing.

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:52.825
That's why we are praying for certain pastors in Miami, because they are already setting up.

00:22:52.826 --> 00:22:55.879
They're already walking by faith. They know what's coming.

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:59.870
I've talked to them on the phone; they already know what's coming.

00:22:59.871 --> 00:23:09.931
God is about to do something huge in Cuba. So you don't wait until it happens. You're not going to be reactive; you're proactive, right?

00:23:09.932 --> 00:23:17.253
So you're already getting your stuff ready because you know what God's about to do in this end-time move.

00:23:17.254 --> 00:23:20.282
You're not going to wait until it happens, because then you're already too late.

00:23:20.283 --> 00:23:29.159
You want to be the forerunners for the greatest move of God we've ever seen in this modern-day era.

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:37.359
Watch what God is about to do with the greatest revival. Ladies and gentlemen, I'm just excited to be a part of it.

00:23:37.360 --> 00:23:42.470
Go ahead and play the video concerning Cuba. Did you find anything about that, son?

00:23:42.471 --> 00:23:49.639
Was the panda bear talking about that? Okay, this is the panda bear.

00:23:49.640 --> 00:24:25.039
When was that? April 30th, two weeks ago. The panda bear is devising a plan of its own with a box.

00:24:25.040 --> 00:24:36.658
The panda bear has a box and is looking over because he doesn't want you to see it.

00:24:36.659 --> 00:24:50.999
He has his head down and he's looking in the box, but he has a plan of his own.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:59.719
He's turning his back on Putin; he's turning his back on everyone else and has a plan by himself.

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:41.553
The evil-looking panda is wrapped in their flag and it's talking to the dragon Kim Jong-un as they gaze upon Taiwan.

00:25:41.554 --> 00:25:58.119
Do you see? I said, 'Yeah, they gaze upon it.'Taiwan is glowing with yellow lights.

00:25:58.120 --> 00:26:19.919
And the panda is licking its lips. The panda is licking its lips—his big long tongue—and he's licking his lips.

00:26:19.920 --> 00:26:33.397
Well, praise the Lord. Father, we just praise you tonight for what you've shown us.

00:26:33.398 --> 00:26:37.477
Lord, we thank you that we will pray over this and continue to pray over this.

00:26:37.478 --> 00:26:46.782
That's when he stopped; that's why I stopped and started. Thank you, Lord.

00:26:46.783 --> 00:26:53.982
Right now, son, it's a good number. Always pray with me; there is so much more time.

00:26:53.983 --> 00:26:56.748
That's when it lifted, because I said they were licking their lips.

00:26:56.749 --> 00:27:05.978
They're about to try to take Taiwan and they'll use North Korea. He was talking to the dragon.

00:27:05.979 --> 00:27:16.159
Every single time I see over North Korea, it's that red dragon wrapped around there. It has tight claws down in those people.

00:27:16.160 --> 00:27:25.608
But that was before I saw the dove, the cardinal, the two black crows, and the turtle.

00:27:25.609 --> 00:27:33.359
The Lord said, 'Look at these.'It was symbolic of different people in Europe.

00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:51.039
So, let's see what they said about Cuba today. Do you have anything real quick?

00:27:51.040 --> 00:28:04.182
Okay, go ahead. Let's listen to Rubio real quick. We're trying to make it quick for y'all.

00:28:04.183 --> 00:28:10.018
'In the case of Cuba, it is a very different situation. There is no economy in Cuba.

00:28:10.019 --> 00:28:15.956
To the extent there's any wealth in Cuba, it doesn't go to the people. It doesn't even go to the government.

00:28:15.957 --> 00:28:20.377
The wealth is controlled by a private company owned by military generals.

00:28:20.378 --> 00:28:23.216
They take all the money; they're sitting on billions of dollars.

00:28:23.217 --> 00:28:30.630
This is a country where people are literally now eating garbage from the streets, but they have a company that controls all of the money-making there.

00:28:30.631 --> 00:28:37.163
That's sitting on 15 to 16 billion dollars. So, it's a broken, non-functional economy and it's impossible to change it.

00:28:37.164 --> 00:28:47.734
I wish it were different, but I believe—it's my personal opinion—you cannot change the economic trajectory of Cuba as long as the people who are in charge of it now are in charge.

00:28:47.735 --> 00:28:50.422
That's what's going to have to change because these people have proven incapable.

00:28:50.423 --> 00:28:54.403
I hope I'm wrong. We'll give them a chance, but I don't think it's going to happen.

00:28:54.404 --> 00:29:08.116
I don't think we're going to be able to change the trajectory of Cuba as long as these people are in charge in that regime.'That's interesting.

00:29:08.117 --> 00:29:24.889
And then the CIA posted this. Now, there was more to what I saw about that and the boxes concerning where they raided the office and then him going to Cuba.

00:29:24.890 --> 00:29:36.119
After they raided the office, they went through it and the Lord said, 'Remember Kennedy? Remember Kennedy? The Kennedy curse?

00:29:36.120 --> 00:29:47.239
Remember Kennedy?'There was something so much darker to this and the Lord would not allow me to release it, especially publicly.

00:29:47.240 --> 00:29:59.993
I will say it like this: it's like Jason Bourne. Go ahead. You have video?

00:29:59.994 --> 00:30:12.679
No, it's not video; it's CIA pictures. They blurred out their faces.

00:30:12.680 --> 00:30:16.742
There are people there gardening. There are things going on.

00:30:16.743 --> 00:30:26.105
The CIA shows up right before, I believe, we invade. Something major is about to go down.

00:30:26.106 --> 00:30:30.826
And when it happens, we'll be on here live praying with you all.

00:30:30.827 --> 00:30:34.559
We'll pray for them. It's going to happen. I'm telling you, it's going to happen.

00:30:34.560 --> 00:30:40.646
I just believe with all my heart that God is about to do something major with this, and people are going to be upset about it.

00:30:40.647 --> 00:30:49.839
Everybody will say, 'Oh well, he's a war criminal'and all these things. But I'm telling you, it's about the revival.

00:30:49.840 --> 00:31:07.108
You're looking at something so small that you can see just on the news and what fake news is telling you, but the bottom line is it's about a liberation of a people to have a major revival. We're running out of time.

00:31:07.109 --> 00:31:23.479
You are still looking at your little plan of what you're going to do with your family—you're going to have a little house on the hill, a little cottage, maybe three or four kids, have a nice little car, your 401k.

00:31:23.480 --> 00:31:38.051
But I'm trying to tell you, Jesus Christ is coming. His main mission right now is to save that which was lost. And we're running out of time.

00:31:38.052 --> 00:31:45.735
Right now He's going into the places that have been secluded, where there are great strongholds of witchcraft.

00:31:45.736 --> 00:31:53.486
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to deal with the witchcraft. I'm going to deal with the witchcraft in Africa. I'm going to deal with the witchcraft in South America.

